text: Oktyabrsky () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Shemyaksky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,663 as of 2010. There are 20 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Ufa. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Oktyabrsky, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
